1
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:03,200
I know your obsession is to hand the evidence

2
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,620
to someone who can punish him,

3
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:06,000
to overturn the Su family's case,

4
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,200
and restore your father's reputation.

5
00:01:25,830 --> 00:01:28,490
What is the meaning of this, Vice Minister Zhou?

6
00:01:28,910 --> 00:01:31,789
General Xie, my servant reported that rebels infiltrated the building.

7
00:01:31,789 --> 00:01:33,620
I was worried about Miss Adeng's safety,

8
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:34,950
so I brought my men here.

9
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:38,250
You come in alone.

10
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:40,860
All of you, step down.

11
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,000
Adeng.

12
00:01:48,450 --> 00:01:50,200
What are you standing there for?

13
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:52,330
Hurry up and get rid of this evil ghost!

14
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:08,660
An official must keep his original intention,

15
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,410
be upright and honest,

16
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:12,660
so as not to fail the people's trust.

17
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:18,000
We must replace the guards at these border fortresses

18
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,500
with our own men.

19
00:02:19,579 --> 00:02:22,000
Once our power completely infiltrates the imperial court,

20
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,870
the world will be in our pockets.

21
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:26,280
Don't worry, Master.

22
00:02:26,290 --> 00:02:27,620
I have already taken care of it.

23
00:02:27,620 --> 00:02:28,790
The Ministry of Revenue's military pay and provisions

24
00:02:28,790 --> 00:02:30,790
are entirely under our control.

25
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,329
All supplies and personnel transfers

26
00:02:32,329 --> 00:02:33,620
are completely at your command,

27
00:02:33,620 --> 00:02:34,950
without any deviation.

28
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,120
Wanniang, I have stumbled upon a shocking conspiracy.

29
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,200
They won't let me go.

30
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,910
Remember, an official must keep his original intention,

31
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:47,829
be upright and honest,

32
00:02:47,829 --> 00:02:49,160
so as not to fail the people's trust.

33
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,700
You must live well.

34
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:03,830
By imperial decree, we are here to search the corrupt traitor Su's residence

35
00:03:03,830 --> 00:03:05,830
and execute everyone in the family!

36
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:08,160
Miss, go!

37
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:44,829
I want to make the last trace of the Su family

38
00:03:44,829 --> 00:03:48,790
completely disappear from this world.

39
00:04:23,250 --> 00:04:25,580
You all must die!

40
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:05,060
The Su family's grievances have finally been cleared.

41
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:08,580
Wanniang didn't let you down.

42
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:24,580
Mr. Su's lifelong reputation for honesty has been preserved,

43
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:27,330
but justice still came late.
